	event. Make it selectable and let it accept hover events. 
	* IggiMainWindow.cc: Add zoom in and zoom out.
	* IggiScene.cc: Add an event group in the main scene.
	* IggiTreeItem.h, IggiTreeItem.cc: Add clear and destroy member
	functions.
	* IggiTreeModel.h, IggiTreeModel.cc: Add a member function to
	clear the model.

